    About us

     

    BOI SERVICES, BASICS OF IMMIGRATION CONSULTANT SERVICES LLP., was set up on a small scale near New Delhi, India in 2012; the plan was to ease the documentation procedure for immigration processes. As we delve into the process of immigration, we discovered a whole new heights, that BOI Services, can create for its clients, by not just
    providing the documentation services but making the entire migration process comfortable, easy and enjoyable for its clients.
              In 2017, BOI Services got registered and a new purpose was born. We received our MCA (MINISTRY OF CORPORATE AFFAIRS) license (AAI-6100) on February 20th, 2017, which was  definitely our first step to be involved into the world of immigration. With a dedicated team, BOI Services provide the best services among the immigration industry, from PRE LANDING to POST LANDING, from BASIC GUIDANCE to SESSION MOCK CALLS; we prepare the applicant for the best.

               Not only THE IMMIGRATION, we serve our clients with TOURIST VISA
    APPLICATIONS, HOLIDAY PACKAGAES, FLIGHT RESERVATIONS, BUSINESS VISAS and many more under the service called “TOURSY” (prn: tour – sie).
               In 2019, BOI Services discovered the need of professional help by their clients, for resume, portfolio, profile build-ups, presentable profiles etc. for better career opportunities overseas and domestic. A new service called “HIREIGHT” (prn: hire – right) was introduced to make the remarkable first impression for the interviews.
